No. 19,

Misc.

Miller v. Biggs, Chief Judge, U. S. Court of Appeals. David H. Kubert for petitioner. Philip W. Amram and Gilbert Hahn, Jr., for respondent. Emil F. Goldhaber, Special Assistant Attorney General of Pennsylvania, filed a memorandum for the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied.
